    "rationale": "Despite multiple credibility factors achieving levels below their required levels, the assessment team accepted the model for VAD use on the basis that Monte Carlo UQ bounds hemolysis predictions below the clinical threshold with 95% confidence. The credibility gaps are noted but judged tolerable given the conservative UQ approach. Note: several factors were assessed without documenting structured acceptance criteria, creating an undocumented basis for the required levels assigned.",
